{
  "texts": [
    "4a, b) in both fresh and frozen tissue datasets.",
    "Portal and central expression signatures were calculated separately across these marker genes in each of the two cell types and datasets.",
    "Z-normalization was done per gene and the portal and central scores represented the sum across normalized portal or central marker gene expressions in a given nucleus or cell.",
    "The signature was then shown on UMAP embeddings of each cell type and processing protocol.",
    "For the frozen tissue dataset, a UMAP embedding containing previously annotated cell types was used."
  ]
}